---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-background-dark/90 backdrop-blur-sm pt-20 pb-10 border-t border-slate-800 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <img src="/fa-logo.png" alt="FreeAgents" class="size-8 shrink-0 rounded-full object-cover" width="32" height="32" />
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-black tracking-tight">FreeAgents</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-500 max-w-xs mb-6">
          El aliado tecnológico de las empresas que no se conforman. Software para el crecimiento real.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h6 class="text-white font-bold mb-6">Quick Links</h6>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-500">
          <li><a href="#soluciones" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Soluciones</a></li>
          <li><a href="#proceso" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Metodología</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contacto" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Contacto</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h6 class="text-white font-bold mb-6">Contacto</h6>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-500">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">mail</span>
            <a href="mailto:hello@freeagents.tech" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">hello@freeagents.tech</a>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">location_on</span>
            Global Operations
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-slate-600 text-sm">
      <p>© {currentYear} FreeAgents. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Privacidad</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Términos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
